  "title": "A big rectangular UFO flying slowly at low altitude in Parobé [2002]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/11/a-big-rectangular-ufo-flying-slowly-at-low-altitude-in-parobe-2002/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-jk",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>SEPT 1st, 2002</strong>. 21h00am. Duration: 10 min. In the city of Parobé, State of Rio Grande do Sul, two witnesses spotted an unidentified rectangular flying object about 40 meters in size, flying at low speed and with little altitude without leaving any trails or displacement trails. The sighting of the two UFOs was carried out under conditions of visibility described as &#8220;good&#8221; from the center of the city.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.626. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário com relato sobre avistamento de ovni no município de Parobé, Rio Grande do Sul&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>SEPT 1st, 2002. 21h00am. Duration: 10 min. In the city of Parobé, State of Rio Grande do Sul, two witnesses spotted an unidentified rectangular flying object about 40 meters in size, flying at low speed and with little altitude without leaving any trails or displacement trails. The sighting of the two UFOs was carried out [&hellip;]</p>\n",
